Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼中尚覺遙遠的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已經來到面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將迅速地成為回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「未來」的表情總是有點不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們就用笑容去迎接她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 早安啊 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我試穿了制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點高興而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也成為正式領航員了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就只有這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩要從領航員業界功成身退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱退的理由不只是那樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩好像很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被邀請擔任鳳尾舟協會的常務理事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅侷限於亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了整個水上觀光業的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓她盡一份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就算艾莉西亞前輩再怎麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法同時兼顧兩份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以好像請他們等到我成為正式領航員以後再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到結婚 其實我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定也是在等待我的晉級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我再認真一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽…說艾莉西亞小姐要…要結婚是真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我這是騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早上開始就有一大堆人打電話來問這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是在哪裡聽到傳聞的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:17.66,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 嶄新的開端…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我熟悉工作之前 艾莉西亞前輩都會留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱退儀式全部都由協會來策劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣啦 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級擔心妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 藍華 愛麗絲 謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從知道艾莉西亞前輩要隱退那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就忙這忙那的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都忙得暈頭轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 艾莉西亞前輩總是面帶笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都仍舊和平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間像往常一樣流逝著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而又幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個數據是什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份文件…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有份文件我不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到處在找妳哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人送花來給我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都不希望艾莉西亞前輩隱退的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人也是…市民也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家其實都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡艾莉西亞前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是水之三大精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家的白雪公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想繼續跟妳在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚停不下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里就已經有能力成為正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在太害怕失去與燈里在一起的這段美好的時光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己身為前輩必須要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我每次…每次都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都因為我太任性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多的事情同時發生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這一切又太過幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是非常值得高興的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論時間或是空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在不斷變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為自己能夠理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心中卻仍舊充滿不安與恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並肩走在一起時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大家走的是同一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實大家都是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在探索著屬於自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在自己的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大家相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想要與在路的前方的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的未來邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得用笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來送走艾莉西亞前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長 今天也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個預約是庵野波平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那是郵遞員叔叔的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天您不用上班嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我已經退休啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就在辦公室做管理的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長久以來真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是蕎麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的稱號是海藍寶石嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能坐在成為正式領航員的小妹妹的鳳尾舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一些交接工作的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩一直都陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…明天的隱退儀式結束以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的變成一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有整個城鎮陪著小妹妹妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後透過郵遞員叔叔的介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也有客人預約了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾位客人是佛洛林咖啡館的店長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(486,440)\fs20}Caffe Florian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鐘樓的管理員先生推薦來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在接受很多人的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里的亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開張了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…亞利亞公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉 你在哭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高興的眼淚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳成為正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到下雪的季節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白雪公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 生奶油可可嗎？好久沒喝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多多的奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩 超級任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦 核桃麵包久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛剛出爐的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿了以前的所有…歡樂的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開這扇門 是我一天中的第一個工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在打開它 平凡的一天就即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這份溫馨的光景…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被冷冽的晨風吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將演繹出「現在」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 之後的大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中郵遞員伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在上班前都會給我送來新鮮的雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他浮島的家中開始養雞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋的年輕分店長 藍華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近開始有了威信 非常地帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只有我們兩個人在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟以前一樣是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說阿魯前段時間也成功晉級了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最近不怎麼見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過藍華都會把他的近況詳細地告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說還長高了一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生也成功晉級了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不知不覺出現在店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得這一定是曉先生特有的關心方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像很閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也到浮島來玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的跳級正式領航員愛麗絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是成為周圍目光的焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而愛麗絲最最熱衷的自我原則呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是三個人一塊去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不三個人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就會毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前輩受到大眾的推舉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間終於在歌劇院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召開了一場個人演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然愛麗絲抱怨她怠慢了領航員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過演唱會當天看到雅典娜前輩那身姿卻感動到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷哭了呢 要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋的晃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在名副其實地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了光芒四射的No.1領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身姿 真可謂是盛情綻放的薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她總是礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要讓我的時代早日到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我知道她心裡肯定因為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃前輩的活躍而高興得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠的白雪公主 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙著出席各式各樣的演講和典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集會和聯歡會等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都忙得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間我還看到了她與祖母一起擔任特邀講師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在時間允許的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又來看妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都像這樣 跟祖母一起來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如水之精靈一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我們露出美麗的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幸福包圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來許多開端的風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果也能送到小愛那裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試穿了制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點高興罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:30.94,END,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,469)\bord0\shad1\fsp6\3c&H475B5F&\4c&H575757&}願那起始之風  吹拂到您身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:38.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.91,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:22.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:28.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:43.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:52.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:04:01.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:06.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:38.92,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾記得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.91,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.04,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.44,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.89,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:22.01,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:28.95,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 嶄露頭角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.31,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠地 充滿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.95,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓人陶醉的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:43.22,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:52.94,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}每個溫暖的 日子往復著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:04:01.36,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不經意間 從那遠方
